RYAN 17:

In the directory where you downloaded SWAT 4, there is a file called "reloaded.nfo", right-click on it, chose "open with", and then your notepad. 

But if you want to do it faster, just enter "My computer", then you right-click on the virtual-drive you have mouted the file, and the chose "explore". In there, it is a directory called "crack", when you have doubleklicked on that there is a file called smething like "rld-k**".. It is an .exe. Doubleklick on  it, than press "generate" on the keygenerator. MAGIC.. there u have your key. Hope it helps.. Otherwise, just PM me.

Cheers
